sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Santa (giver)
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as API
  participant DB as DB
  participant R as Recipient
  Note over S,R: Anonymity preserved via conversation token/channel

  S->>FE: Send anonymous question
  FE->>API: POST /messages {groupId, threadId, text}
  API->>DB: Store message (senderId hidden from R)
  API-->>R: Notify (email/push) via relay
  R->>FE: Reply anonymously
  FE->>API: POST /messages {threadId, text}
  API->>DB: Store reply & relay to S